305
00:11:05,020 --> 00:11:05,820
I mean... I...

306
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,860
Stop it.

307
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:08,580
Look how worried Yunzhang is.

308
00:11:09,540 --> 00:11:10,460
Nonsense.

309
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,700
