340
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:42,940
No.

341
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:43,940
I didn't do it before.

342
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:44,740
You're such a fool.

343
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:45,820
Think about it.

344
