is impotent.

377
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:07,740
You're impotent!

378
00:14:13,180 --> 00:14:14,020
What to do?

379
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:16,700
Yunzhang.

380
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:21,460
Yunzhang.

