and tear up the Empress Dowager's decree.

408
00:15:30,180 --> 00:15:31,180
I can't bear it!

409
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:32,820
So what if you can't bear it?

410
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:37,420
Liu Xie,

411
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:38,820
