00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:46,500
Our deal has just begun.

415
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,500
Why are you so anxious?

416
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:49,340
What about Jinfeng?

417
00:15:55,580 --> 00:15:57,620
Do you think there is a better choice for Jinfeng

