454
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:52,300
How so?

455
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:53,700
I'm not even embarrassed yet.

456
00:17:54,260 --> 00:17:55,100
All right then.

457
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:07,980
Where's your treasure?

458
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:10,420
