483
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:54,180
Oh, no!

484
00:18:54,180 --> 00:18:55,300
What Eunuch Bai?

485
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:56,620
What a waste of effort!

486
00:18:57,780 --> 00:18:58,940
